posting_body: ['Nantucket Apartments in Santa Clara, CA', 'Nantucket Apartments offers you a unique living experience unparalleled by any other apartment community.', 'With beautifully designed landscaped gardens create the feeling of a quiet, intimate neighborhood.', 'We are located right next door to Lick Mill Park and within walking distance of cycling and jogging trails along the Guadalupe River, and many new shops and restaurants.', 'With our fitness center, full service business center, billiards parlor, Parcel Pending Lockers, pool side Wi-Fi, car wash area, Nantucket has everything you’re looking for in a home.', 'Broker License #01525033', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 62', 'OR Text', '62', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our leasing team.', 'Use this link for more info:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 830-856 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Fireplace*', '- In unit laundry room*', '- Renovated Interiors', '- Non-Smoking', '- ALL Appliances', '- Washer/Dryers', 'Community Amenities', '- Gated Community', '- Package Receiving', '- Garden Areas', '- Planned Community Activities', '- Spa', '- Billiards Table', '- Dry Cleaning Services', '- Free Wi-fi in Common Areas', '- Swimming Pool', '- Fitness Center', '- Car Wash Area', '- Basketball Court', '- Business Center', '- Controlled Access Entry Building', 'Pet Policy', 'WE ARE PET FRIENDLY!', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Sunday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Nantucket', '1600 Nantucket Circle, Santa Clara, CA, 95054', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'AMC-CA, Inc. dba Apartment Management Consultants-BRE #01525033', 'GgDJk9hjSYgi']
